name: Void Runner
description:
Go higher up in the sky while listening to exciting music tracks . The higher you go in less time the higher score you get . falling might take you back to the zero point if you're not careful !
The world is a mix between earth and void , and you as a parkour runner can take advantage of that to climb and go high in the sky , to explore new and mysterious areas , and reach the outer space !
Leaderboard is based on your total time to reach the end. You can run, slide , crawl, vault , parkour , slow time , fall ! but make sure you get back up again to get to the top of that leaderboard .
